  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tip</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the course of the game, mastering the high frequency of rolling skill is an excellent strategy to avoid the attack of the enemy. This skill can greatly reduce the challenge of the game and help you more easily move between the battlefield. Make good use of rolling action, not only can skillfully dodge the enemy's attack, but also for you to win the precious counterattack time, is an indispensable part of the game strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a wonderful horizontal version of the action game, the player is in full control of a heroic character, free to use a coherent combination of moves, wielding a variety of sharp weapons, unleashing stunning skills, all the way through, skillfully avoiding or destroying potential traps, and bravely battle the death of the zombie swarm. The game is carefully equipped with a rich variety of sound effects and realistic voice for the protagonist, and strive to create an immersive, exciting game atmosphere for players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight & Combo</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through clever run-up acceleration, agile jumps, and smooth tumbling skills, players can activate a variety of powerful combo boxing skills to display the art of combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa79f6870a7786553d277d9bb5.poster.avif?t=1732849978\" width=674 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa79f6870a7786553d277d9bb5.webm?t=1732849978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa79f6870a7786553d277d9bb5.mp4?t=1732849978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With precise run-up accumulators, flexible jumps and consistent tumbling movements, players can unlock and execute a series of unique and powerful boxing combinations that make the battle full of surprises and changes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/f750d8c214c21b6ce8e8e26e3a99534c.poster.avif?t=1732849978\" width=674 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/f750d8c214c21b6ce8e8e26e3a99534c.webm?t=1732849978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/f750d8c214c21b6ce8e8e26e3a99534c.mp4?t=1732849978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich role skin</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Provide a variety of character skin options, each of which is unique, bringing a new look to the player's visual experience, highlighting the personality.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/9e0d7491073ea2b90650f8a557d9d5d6.avif?t=1732849978\" width=766 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tip</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the course of the game, mastering the high frequency of rolling skill is an excellent strategy to avoid the attack of the enemy. This skill can greatly reduce the challenge of the game and help you more easily move between the battlefield. Make good use of rolling action, not only can skillfully dodge the enemy's attack, but also for you to win the precious counterattack time, is an indispensable part of the game strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a wonderful horizontal version of the action game, the player is in full control of a heroic character, free to use a coherent combination of moves, wielding a variety of sharp weapons, unleashing stunning skills, all the way through, skillfully avoiding or destroying potential traps, and bravely battle the death of the zombie swarm. The game is carefully equipped with a rich variety of sound effects and realistic voice for the protagonist, and strive to create an immersive, exciting game atmosphere for players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight & Combo</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through clever run-up acceleration, agile jumps, and smooth tumbling skills, players can activate a variety of powerful combo boxing skills to display the art of combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa79f6870a7786553d277d9bb5.poster.avif?t=1732849978\" width=674 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa79f6870a7786553d277d9bb5.webm?t=1732849978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/906680/extras/805931fa7